title: Life in Cold Blood - s01e05 - Armoured Giants (BBC TV 1)
description:
Life in Cold Blood - 5/5 - Armoured Giants


Mon 3 Mar, 9:00 pm - 10:00 pm


David Attenborough meets reptile heavyweights - the tortoises, turtles and crocodiles, showing what it&#039;s like to live within a suit of armour and revealing a dynamic, warm and caring side to these ancient giants. Mating giant tortoises fit together like spoons, green turtles passionately mate in tropical seas, a mother spectacled caiman rescues a huge creche of babies and sophisticated saltwater crocodiles ambush fish just like bears catching salmon.
